# Patch to warpdotdev/warp: allow http URLs to loopback hosts in custom AI endpoint settings
# Base: 466d1856c1bc1824e8680ce77436691d1b4977bf (warp@master)
# Patched: 097fbe304efa06fd07fa5376f375752e1e75475e
# License: AGPL-3.0-or-later (inherited from warpdotdev/warp)
